title: things i am sure harry styles does when you’ve been dating long enough.
body:
1. kiss your ears. like a lot.

2. call you ‘kiddo’ instead of making effort for cute nicknames. 

3. sleep with your sweater when you’re not home because it smells like you. 

4. sing while making pancakes in the morning. 

5. wanting to kiss after you’ve just put on lipstick. 

6. take care of you when you’re sick. 

7. always buy you tampons because he likes to be ready for the monster you become every month. 

8. play with your earrings all the time. 

9. set alarm for five minutes early so he can make sure to cuddle with you. 

10. never let you be the little spoon when you’re awake but switch after you’ve fallen asleep. 

11. say ‘sorry love’ every time he has to switch on the light really late or super early. 

12. make a song about anything. and i mean literally anything. 

13. read fanfic with you. 

14. console you after your favourite character dies. 

15. shamelessly cry while watching the notebook. 

16. dance with you on all the routines to dirty dancing. 

17. make sure you both sleep naked. 

18. tell you the story behind all his tattoos when you can’t sleep. 

19. prepare for dates where you both lie in fields and cackle unnecessarily. 

20. click photos of you while sleeping to use as his phone wallpaper. 

21. take you to pride parades and dance too much. 

22. tell you he loves you and then lick your face every night.
